modules.description: Handles HTTP requests and responses using the Curl library, supporting GET, POST, and header manipulation. Operates on strings, byte arrays, and custom HTTP message structures. Used to fetch remote data, submit forms, and interact with RESTful APIs in networked applications.

Provides functions for executing HTTP queries with support for caching, SSL client authentication, and debugging. Operates with HTTP request and response data, cache implementations, and SSL certificate configurations. Used to fetch remote resources while managing cached responses and secure connections.
